# raw-passthrough demo: single-line mermaid features without dedicated mmdlog syntax.
@diagram sequence
!+participant U as User
!+participant A as App
!+participant DB as Database
+autonumber
+U->>A: login
+Note over U,A: session check
+A->>DB: load profile
+Note right of DB: lookup by id
+DB->>A: profile
+A--xU: 401 (denied path shown)
+A->>U: welcome
